  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    A[High External Osmolarity] --> B[Water Efflux from Cell]\n    B --> C[Decreased Turgor Pressure]\n\n    C --> F[Mechanosensitive Channels Activation]\n    C --> G[KdpFABC Sensor Activation]\n    C --> AY{Is Turgor Loss Significant?}\n\n    D[Low Intracellular K+ concentration] --> H[TrkA K+ Transporter Activation]\n    F --> AI[K+ Influx via Channels/Transporters]\n    G --> AI\n    H --> AI\n    AI --> R[Intracellular K+ Accumulation]\n    R --> AU{Is K+ Accumulation Sufficient?}\n\n    AY --> |Yes| L[RpoS Activation/Stabilization]\n    AY --> |Yes| K[CosR Activation/Expression]\n    L --> AW{Is RpoS Activated AND CosR Activated?}\n    K --> AW\n\n    E[Environmental signals for PhoP/Q] --> I[PhoQ Sensor Kinase Activation]\n    I --> J[PhoP Response Regulator Phosphorylation]\n    J --> AX{Is PhoP Phosphorylated AND Osmotic Stress Present?}\n\n    AW --> AJ[Transcription of Osmoprotective Genes]\n    AX --> AJ\n    AJ --> AK[Translation of Osmoprotective Proteins]\n\n    G --> S[KdpFABC Expression]\n    S --> AK\n\n    AU --> |No, need more| AV{Are External Compatible Solutes Available?}\n    AU --> |Yes, but also| AO[Compatible Solute Accumulation]\n\n    AV --> |Yes| M[BetT/ProU/ProP Transporter Sensing]\n    M --> Y[Choline Uptake]\n    M --> Z[Betaine Uptake]\n    M --> AA[Proline Uptake]\n\n    Y --> AC(\\1)\n    AC --> P[BetA/BetB Enzyme Activity]\n    P --> AL[Choline Oxidation to Betaine]\n    AL --> AF(\\1)\n    Z --> AF\n    AA --> AE(\\1)\n\n    AV --> |No, synthesize internally| AB[Glutamate Pool]\n    AB --> O[ProB/ProA/ProC Enzyme Activity]\n    O --> AM[Glutamate Conversion to Proline]\n    AM --> AE\n\n    AV --> |No, synthesize internally| N[OtsA/OtsB Enzyme Activity]\n    N --> AN[Glucose-6P & Glucose-1P to Trehalose]\n    AN --> AD(\\1)\n\n    AF --> AO\n    AE --> AO\n    AD --> AO\n    AO --> BB[Restored Turgor Pressure]\n    AO --> BC[Maintained Cell Volume]\n    AO --> BD[Enhanced Macromolecular Stability]\n    AO --> AQ[Protein Protection]\n    AO --> AR[DNA Protection]\n\n    AJ --> T[Bet Operon Expression]\n    T --> P\n    AJ --> U[ProP/ProU/PutP Expression]\n    U --> M\n    AJ --> V[OtsA/OtsB Gene Expression]\n    V --> N\n    AJ --> W[ProB/ProA/ProC Gene Expression]\n    W --> O\n    AJ --> X[BetA/BetB Gene Expression]\n    X --> P\n\n    AY --> AZ{Is Ubiquinone Synthesis Pathway Activated?}\n    AW --> AZ\n\n    AZ --> |Yes| Q[Ubiquinone Biosynthesis Pathway Activation]\n    Q --> AG[Ubiquinone Precursors]\n    AG --> AT[Ubiquinone Synthesis]\n    AT --> AH[Ubiquinone Pool]\n    AH --> AP[Membrane Stabilization]\n    AP --> BA[Increased Osmotic Stress Tolerance]\n    AP --> BD\n\n    BB --> BE[Cell Survival & Growth]\n    BC --> BE\n    BD --> BE\n    BA --> BE\n    AQ --> BD\n    AR --> BD\n    AK --> AS[Metabolic Flux Rerouting]\n    AS --> BE\n\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style B fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style G fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AY fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style H fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AI fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style R fill:#000000,color:#fff\n    style AU fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AW fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style I fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style J fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AX fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AJ fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AK fill:#ffa726,color:#fff\n    style S fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AV fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AO fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style M fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style Y fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Z fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AA fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\